Package: SteppedPower
Type: Package
Title: sample size calculation in longitudinal settings with focus on stepped wedge designs
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Philipp Mildenberger
Maintainer: Philipp Mildenberger <pmildenb@uni-mainz.de>
Description: SteppedPower offers options for power calculation as well 
    as sample size calculation (by the use of uniroot() ) for 
    longitudinal mixed model settings. 
    All calculations are oracle estimates i.e. assume random effect variances 
    to be known (or guessed) in advance. 
